name: Geoff Gallante - Boy On The Moon CD (AUTOGRAPHED)
description:
Geoff Gallante's first album. Playing trumpet, flugelhorn, and piano, Geoff offers his take on beautiful songs about the moon. 

Each CD is autographed by Geoff.

Geoff Gallante - Trumpet, and Flugel Horn
Jean Baptiste - Piano
Michael Bowie - Bass
